title: Peter Grimes - Benjamin Britten - Peter Pears 1969
description:
A classic production of Britten opera conducted by the composer.

Peter Pears (Grimes), Heather Harper (Ellen Orford), Bryan Drake (Balstrode), Elizabeth Bainbridge (Auntie), Owen Brannigan (Swallow) & Robert Tear (Rev Adams)
Staged by Joan Cross
London Symphony Orchestra conducted by Benjamin Britten.
